   Pelosi Orders Impeachment Probe: ‘No One Is above The Law’

Pelosi Orders Impeachment Probe: ‘No One Is above The Law’

     * 24 September 2019
     * AP News

   House Speaker Nancy Pelosi launched the House into a formal impeachment
   inquiry against President Donald Trump, acquiescing to mounting
   pressure from fellow Democrats and plunging a deeply divided nation
   into an election year clash between Congress and the commander in
   chief.

   St. Paul Police Release Video of Fatal Shooting

St. Paul Police Release Video of Fatal Shooting

     * 24 September 2019
     * AP News

   A man carrying a raised knife charged at a St. Paul police officer
   after rear-ending his squad car and refused repeated commands to drop
   the weapon before the officer fatally shot him, according to
   body-camera footage.

   Did Viral Images Show People Climbing a Border Fence That Trump Said
