   border fence.

   Dershowitz Seeks to Throw Out Lawsuit Against Him by Epstein Accuser

Dershowitz Seeks to Throw Out Lawsuit Against Him by Epstein Accuser

     * 24 September 2019
     * AP News

   Harvard law professor Alan Dershowitz has asked a federal judge to
   throw out a lawsuit that accuses him of lying about his sexual history
   with a woman who claims she was a teenage victim of a Jeffrey Epstein
   sex trafficking ring.
